*.tsbuildinfo

# Rust
target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock is COMMITTED (reproducible binary builds via napi-rs)

# napi-rs build outputs
*.node
prebuilds/
# napi's generated JS binding is disabled (--js false) and its generated .d.ts is redirected to
# target/ (ignored above); the committed loader is the hand-written index.js/index.d.ts (F1).

